<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=646&amp;p=671#p671"><![CDATA[
8/25(Thu)9 Taiwanese rescued from Cambodian human trafficking ring/Unprecedented Rainstorm in South Korea (Host: Gal)<br /><br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:05 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:05-7:40 pm Session 1: Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Individual Presentation<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-8:40: Session 2: Group Discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Individual Presentation<br /><br />We will hold a zoom meeting only.<br /><br />Zoom meeting: Please click the link below<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ...<br />Meeting ID:929 8726 6213<br />Password:112233<br /><br />Session I<br />9 Taiwanese rescued from Cambodian human trafficking ring<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.taiwannews.com.tw/en/news/4626546">https://www.taiwannews.com.tw/en/news/4626546</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br />1.What do you think about the main reason that so many Taiwanese trapped in overseas work scams? <br />2.Do you think the COVID-19 pandemic having the effect to facilitate fraud?<br />3.Do you, your family or friends have any experience or lose money in a fraud call or any kind of scams?<br />4.Do you have any good idea about avoiding a scam?<br /><br />----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br /><br />Session II<br />Unprecedented Rainstorm in South Korea<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://thediplomat.com/2022/08/unprecedented-rainstorm-exposes-south-koreas-blind-spots/">https://thediplomat.com/2022/08/unprece ... ind-spots/</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br />1.Have you ever seen or heard about any severe climate change recently in a global scale?<br />2.People said that Taiwan has 4 distinctive seasons this year. Do you agree?<br />3.Do you notice any strange climate change in Taiwan?<br />4.Do you know how to prevent climate change from getting worse?<br /><br />P.S.<br />1.參加三次(含實體及線上會議)後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />2.請帶著開放的心與熱情來參加全英文會話聚會!<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=38674">Louie Wang</a> — Sat Aug 20, 2022 2:37 pm</p><hr />
